Articles.Content:
Been looking for this mod for about a week now.

Spent maybe 5-7 hours searching the forums and any other place I think I would've found it.

It had three parts: a battery pack, an engine, and solar panels that deployed to recharge the battery and IIRC they also controlled the thrust of the engine.

It isnt MMI or the deep space pack.

Only thing I can think of is that it has been removed or deleted.
Sounds like the Void Bukerneering parts that Kreuzung made as an example for the old electrical energy plugin.
